    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cats have been kidnapped by your brother and now they're in danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Massi vs. José</strong> is a reimagination of the first adventure of <strong>Massi</strong>, released back in 2016. Be ready to test your skills by beating <strong>40 levels</strong> filled with coins and collectibles. There are a variety of different platforms that will shape your journey through all the <strong>8 worlds</strong> of this game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful pixel art, expressive animations and stunning visual effects.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 worlds with different themes</strong>, each one with <strong>5 levels</strong>. That's a total of <strong>40 levels</strong> to explore and get <strong>3 stars</strong> in each one of them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab the <strong>key</strong> in each level to go to the next!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock <strong>achievements</strong> and climb the <strong>leaderboards</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller support</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cloud Save:</strong> don't lose your progress!</p></li></ul>",
